    {% spaceless %}
        Tuscaloosa City Schools Transfer Application Confirmation: {{ confirmation }}
    {% endspaceless %}
{% endblock subject %}

{% block body_text %}
Hi {{ email }},

You recently submitted an Accountability Act Transfer Form stating that you intend to transfer to a qualifying non-public Alabama school that is willing to accept the student.  Thank you for providing this information to us.

Please note that you will be required to provide proof of residency to the TCS Attendance Office in order to complete this process.

Please download and print the Accountability Act Transfer Form you will need for a qualifying non-public school in Alabama that can accept the student.

https://choice.tuscaloosacityschools.com/downloads/Accountability_Transfer_Form_2018.docx

For future reference, your confirmation # is {{ confirmation }}. Please retain a copy of this email for your records.

This is an automated email message from a mailbox that does not accept replies.  If you have questions about the application process, please call 205.759.3700 between 8:30 a.m. and 4:00 p.m., Monday through Friday.

Thanks,
Tuscaloosa City Schools
